title: The Real Housewives Of Beverly Hills S04E04 Irked At Cirque WEB-
description:
Ep 4: Irked At Cirque
 While mastering circus school, Brandi and Kyle face off over bullying accusations and Joyce and Lisa butt heads.

Hoping for an afternoon of fun, Kim invites the ladies to a funky and colorful circus school, but tensions simmer as Brandi believes Kyle has labeled her a bully to the tabloids. Later, Lisa suddenly finds herself in the drama when an accusation by Joyce leaves her and the other ladies totally baffled.
